flowRoot.flowPara: OK, now we've got your attention! Are you interested in Technology, Robotics, Programming, Classic Videogames, Electronics or Mechanics?
If so, you should probably check out HACMan, Manchester's Hackspace Group!
We meet three times a month at MadLab[1], in Manchester's Northern Quarter, and spend most of the time chatting, soldering, breaking things, fixing things, and drinking.

Our evening meetings take place from 7pm on the 2nd & 4th Wednesday every month, and our daytime meeting is on the 3rd Saturday of every month, from 10am. Don't worry, there's no entry fee or anything, we just ask for donations towards drinks.
